      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "So they feared the Lord — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Worshipped him externally in that way which the Israelites had used: having and serving gods of their own besides. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And made unto themselves of the lowest of them priests, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "&c. — See note on ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 12:31",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Which sacrificed in the high places —",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Unto the true God; for as to the worship of their own gods, they needed no instruction, and would not permit a person of another religion to minister therein.",
        "children": []
